Care Quality Commission (CQC) 
http://www.cqc.org.uk/  

 
The CQC is the independent regulator of health and adult social care in England. They make 

sure health and social care services provide people with safe, effective, compassionate, 
high-quality care and encourage care services to improve. 

 

 

https://www.bda.uk.com/foodfacts/home
