Contact a Family 
http://www.cafamily.org.uk/  

 
Contact a Family is a national charity for families with disabled children. 

They provide information, advice and support, bringing families together so they can 
support each other. They campaign to improve their circumstances, and for their right to be 

included and equal in society. 
 

 
 

 
